{"id":"amem-48","content_hash":"db74809ffc3ddc019c82af3aa6c72d2b37a2df58091bee729e950f952a4a2f78","title":"Add --any and --all flags to amem search for union vs intersection control","description":"Currently amem search uses AND logic (intersection) for multiple keywords - all terms must be present. Add --any (OR/union) and --all (AND/intersection) flags to let users control this behavior. --any should be the default (breaking change from current behavior).","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2025-10-28T23:01:16.328751-07:00","updated_at":"2025-10-29T10:20:50.568005-07:00","closed_at":"2025-10-29T10:20:50.568005-07:00"}
